  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Roll out tiropita dough to a thickness of 1/8 inch.",
    "In a bowl, mix crumbled feta cheese, chopped piquant peppers, smoked paprika, Greek herbs, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Spread the feta mixture evenly over the dough, leaving a 1/2 inch border around the edges.",
    "Fold the edges of the dough up over the filling, pressing gently to seal.",
    "Brush the top of the tiropita with a little water and sprinkle with a pinch of salt.",
    "Bake for 25-30 minutes, or until golden brown.",
    "Serve warm, sliced into wedges."
